{t:"Paid Search",badge:"BIGGEST IMPROVEMENT",
html:`<div class="ba-grid"><div class="ba-col before"><div class="ba-header">BEFORE</div><div class="ba-item">Relied on UTM tags on landing page</div><div class="ba-item">If utm_medium=cpc present = paid</div><div class="ba-item">If tags missing = hard to identify</div></div>
