{t:'"But how can data be better overall but look different for my site?"',isQ:1,
html:`<div class="client-block"><div class="client-says">CLIENT ASKS:</div><div style="color:var(--white);font-size:15px;margin-bottom:12px">"If the data improved, why does my site's split look so different?"</div>
