<div class="callout blue"><div class="c-icon">📊</div><div><div class="c-title">The key point</div><div class="c-text">The overall methodology is demonstrably more accurate when measured statistically. Each individual site's data reflects a more precise classification of that site's specific traffic. The direction and magnitude of change varies by site, because the traffic profile varies by site.</div></div></div>
<p class="prose">If a client wants to understand their specific data, offer to look at it together.</p>`,
search:"individual site cohort different split better overall methodology accurate"},

{t:'"Was my previous analysis wrong?"',isQ:1,
html:`<div class="client-block"><div class="client-says">CLIENT ASKS:</div><div style="color:var(--white);font-size:15px;margin-bottom:12px">"Does this mean everything I reported last quarter was wrong?"</div>
